        <updateDate>2020-02-13T20:45:02Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This resolution condemns the rise of anti-Semitic attacks and calls on law enforcement officials to hold perpetrators accountable. The resolution also encourages public schools to teach about the history of anti-Semitism, the Holocaust, and the historic importance of the creation of the Jewish State of Israel.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
